activities:
Aptible collects account and profile information, user content, web logs and analytics information, and cookies from users when they use the Aptible services.

Aptible uses that information to:
- Provide, operate, maintain, improve, personalize, and promote our services;
- Develop new products, services, features, and functionality;
- Enable users to access and use our services;
- Process and complete transactions, and send users related information, including purchase confirmations and invoices;
- Communicate with users, including responding to comments, questions, and requests; providing customer service and support; providing users with information about services, including technical notices, updates, security alerts, administrative messages, or advertising or marketing messages; and providing other news or information about us and our select partners;
- Monitor and analyze trends, usage, and activities in connection with our services; and
- Investigate and prevent fraudulent transactions, unauthorized access to our services, and other illegal activities.
